issue.title: Integrate bot analytics
issue.body: Twilio is a supported platform for http://botanalytics.co/. Would be awesome to have analytics from the getgo. I hope it doesn't affect performance too much, but try the integration and we'll evaluate how useful it is

issue.title: 'Remind me later' feature
issue.body: Users can ask Spark to remind them about ordering later. If they don't suggest a specific time, we suggest canned reminder times (maybe the same suggested times as Apple uses when they want to install something that requires a restart?)

issue.title: 'Recurring order' feature
issue.body: Allow users to setup a recurring order that we process automatically. We'll need to know their order, interval they want it, what to do if their order is out of stock

issue.body: Investigate and bookmark https://smsinbox.net/ for merchant-facing use; would this be an easy hack to not have to build our own merchant-dashboard?

issue.title: Watch bots + machine learning talk from Wit.ai competitor (30mins)
issue.body:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HIWqGc7AvKI I know I know, 30 mins. Trust me it's incredibly relevant to us. I hate homework as much as the next guy but I promise it's hella important. 
 
[Alan Nichol](https://twitter.com/alanmnichol) is CTO of [rasa.ai](https://rasa.ai/), a competitor to Wit.ai. I'm not doing a TL;DR because it's important enough that you watch it yourself I PROMISE IT'S GOOD
